dct_description_sm: Military topographic maps. Relief shown by contours, shading, and spot heights. Name of jurisdiction[s] covered by sheet quadrangle appears in upper margin at left, e.g.: Provint͡sii͡a Farakh -- Provint͡sii Gilʹmend, Nimroz. May include name and province of neighboring country. Name of jurisdiction[s] covered by sheet quadrangle appears in upper margin at left, e.g.: Провинция Фарах -- Провинции Гильменд, Нимроз. May include name and province of neighboring country. Common title precedes jurisdiction name at upper left on each sheet. Sheets individually subtitled and numbered (with roman-alphabet lettering) in upper margin, e.g.: Kotalak, H-41-IV -- Vasp, I-41-XXIX. Sheets individually subtitled and numbered (with roman-alphabet lettering) in upper margin, e.g.: Коталак, H-41-IV -- Васп, I-41-XXIX. Ed./publication date in upper border at right, e.g.: Izdanie 1980 g. -- Izdanie 1986 g. -- Izdanie 1988 g. Ed./publication date in upper border at right, e.g.: Издание 1980 г. -- Издание 1986 г. -- Издание 1988 г. Includes notes, diagrams, and compilation date[s] in lower margin. Blue sheet no. in upper margin precedes black sheet no., e.g.: 08-41-01 -- 09-42-13. Text and ancillary map, "Skhema gruntov," on verso. Text and ancillary map, "Схема грунтов," on verso.
